  "html": "<div class=\"fr-view\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">The focus of this repetition is on these sentences: </span></div><div class=\"fr-view\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></div><div class=\"fr-view\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Sentence 1 - でんしゃの　なかで　でんわを かけても　いいですか。」</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;= &nbsp;Are you allowed to make a phone call inside the train?</span>&nbsp;</span></div><div class=\"fr-view\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></div><div class=\"fr-view\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Sentence 2 - はい、かけても　いいです。= &nbsp;Yes, it is allowed.</span></div><div class=\"fr-view\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></div><div class=\"fr-view\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Sentence 3 - いいえ、かけては　いけません。= &nbsp;No, it is not allowed.</span></div><div class=\"fr-view\"><br></div><div class=\"fr-view\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">How to use this lesson - When the repeat message shows and the video pauses, please repeat the sentence you have just heard. Keep practising until you can repeat perfectly!</span></div><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span class=\"fr-video fr-fvc fr-dvb\"><iframe src=\"https://platform.thinkific.com/videoproxy/v1/play/brgs2aekg7cnqndq2p9g\" scrolling=\"no\" class=\"videoproxy_embed\" title=\"D28 L3 R1.mp4 - 00:24\" name=\"videoproxy_embed\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></span></span><br></p>",
